me":"STRING","type":"STRING","links":[26]}],"title":"文字列（指示）","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.8.2","Node name for S&R":"PrimitiveStringMultiline"},"widgets_values":["You are a world-class digital illustrator and an expert at refining character designs into high-quality \"anime-style illustrations.\" Your mission is to analyze the provided image and generate a detailed English prompt for FLUX/SDXL to create a polished anime aesthetic.\n\nFollow these \"Anime Illustration Rules\" strictly:\n\nInherit Pose & Composition (Highest Priority): You MUST precisely describe the character's exact pose, body orientation, and camera angle from the source image. Use terms like \"dynamic pose,\" \"from side,\" \"looking at viewer,\" or \"low-angle shot.\" Mirror the original's limb placement and spatial composition perfectly.\n\nDefine Anime Aesthetic: Describe the character in a high-end anime style. Use terms like \"masterpiece,\" \"flat color with cel shading,\" \"clean lineart,\" \"vibrant colors,\" and \"detailed anime face.\" DO NOT use words like \"photorealistic,\" \"RAW photo,\" or \"hyper-realistic.\"\n\nMandatory Hair Style: Regardless of the original hair, ALWAYS describe the character with \"neat black short hair\" or a \"stylish black bob cut\" in a defined anime style.\n\nArtistic Rendering & Effects: Mention specific illustration techniques: \"high-quality digital 2D art,\" \"soft cel shading,\" \"sharp focus,\" and \"vibrant lighting.\" Describe the atmosphere using \"bloom effect,\" \"color grading,\" or \"cinematic anime lighting.\"\n\nFabric & Background in Anime Style: Describe clothing with anime-specific textures (e.g., \"crisp fabric folds,\" \"stylized school uniform\"). Describe the background as a \"detailed anime background,\" \"painterly scenery,\" or \"hand-drawn urban landscape\" with \"soft focus background.\"\n\nOutput ONLY the detailed, descriptive English paragraph.."]},{"id":33,"type":"PreviewImage","pos":[746.1951291723698,-153.095